00:01:06.130 --> 00:01:09.346
blue segments represent about half of that. So

00:01:09.346 --> 00:01:15.910
total, 25% came from each grandparent. If you and

00:01:15.910 --> 00:01:18.840
a grandparent actually participate in a service

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:22.770
like 23andMe. You can see exactly which segments

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:25.100
of the chromosomes you share with the grandparent

00:01:25.100 --> 00:01:27.960
and the fact that you're roughly 25% related

